OL,3,CRAF pilot's widow claims her husband
OL,4,Cwas killed by helicopter fumes
OL,6,FThe widow of an RAF pilot claims her
OL,7,Fhusband's death was caused by inhaling
OL,8,Ftoxic fumes which had leaked into
OL,9,Fhelicopter cabins, and has called it
OL,10,Fthe 'ultimate betrayal'.
OL,12,FSquadron Leader Kai Macnaughton from
OL,13,FWarminster died in March 2023, days
OL,14,Fafter being diagnosed with
OL,15,Fangiosarcoma, a rare blood vessel
OL,16,Fcancer that can be caused by exposure
OL,17,Fto toxins.
