OL,3,CRAF pilot's widow claims her husband
OL,4,Cwas killed by helicopter fumes
OL,6,F"He died so quickly; it's still quite
OL,7,Fshocking because it just came from
OL,8,Fnowhere," says his widow, Clare, who
OL,9,Fdescribes her husband's death as
OL,10,Fhorrific. "He seemed to melt from the
OL,11,Finside."
OL,13,FClare Macnaughton is one of around 40
OL,14,Fpeople taking legal action against the
OL,15,Fgovernment, with their lawyers
OL,16,Fclaiming carcinogenic fumes from
OL,17,Fhelicopter exhausts circulated in the
OL,18,Fcabins of older models such as the Sea
OL,19,FKing and Wessex. Aircraft which are no
OL,20,Flonger used by the RAF.
