OL,3,CRAF pilot's widow claims her husband
OL,4,Cwas killed by helicopter fumes
OL,6,FKai Macnaughton, 53, and a father of
OL,7,Ftwo, had spent 30 years in the
OL,8,Fmilitary and had flown thousands of
OL,9,Fhours in helicopters, including over
OL,10,FAfghanistan and Iraq.
OL,12,F"It's the ultimate betrayal", says
OL,13,FClare. "Kai would have taken a bullet
OL,14,Ffor his country. But he would never
OL,15,Fhave signed up for an angiosarcoma. He
OL,16,Fexpected the military to protect him,
OL,17,For give him the tools to protect
OL,18,Fhimself."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
