OL,3,CRAF pilot's widow claims her husband
OL,4,Cwas killed by helicopter fumes
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence told ITV News
OL,7,Fthat it can't comment on individual
OL,8,Fcases, but did say, "We continually
OL,9,Freview our policies to ensure they are
OL,10,Faligned with good practice and protect
OL,11,Four people from harm.
OL,13,F"Service personnel and veterans who
OL,14,Fbelieve they have suffered ill health
OL,15,Fdue to service have the right to apply
OL,16,Ffor no-fault compensation under the
OL,17,FArmed Forces Compensation Scheme."
OL,19,FClare Macnaughton is pursuing a
OL,20,Fcompensation claim under that scheme,
OL,21,Fas well as taking further legal action.
