OL,3,CRAF pilot's widow claims her husband
OL,4,Cwas killed by helicopter fumes
OL,6,FIn 2022, the Institute of Naval
OL,7,FMedicine Toxicologist was asked to
OL,8,Finvestigate if there were any links
OL,9,Fbetween exposure to Sea King
OL,10,Fhelicopter exhaust fumes and the
OL,11,Flikelihood of developing a sarcoma. It
OL,12,Ffound no documented evidence.
OL,14,FMinisters have since asked the
OL,15,FIndependent Medical Expert Group to re-
OL,16,Fexamine the evidence around the issue.
OL,17,FTheir findings will be set-out in
OL,18,Ftheir next report, due to be published
OL,19,Fthis summer.
